      "cookedHtml": "<h2><a name=\"p-184733-h-20x20uploade6spwpowqoqtrtuz5rsxfdrgijvpng-save-the-date-experience-elevate-like-never-before-20x20uploade6spwpowqoqtrtuz5rsxfdrgijvpng-1\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-184733-h-20x20uploade6spwpowqoqtrtuz5rsxfdrgijvpng-save-the-date-experience-elevate-like-never-before-20x20uploade6spwpowqoqtrtuz5rsxfdrgijvpng-1\"></a><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/6/2/62e577082cfeb3eee5aab782c06bfd1ecc58e3cd.png\" alt=\"🎉\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong>Save the date &amp; experience Elevate like never before</strong> <img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/6/2/62e577082cfeb3eee5aab782c06bfd1ecc58e3cd.png\" alt=\"🎉\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></h2>\n<h4><a name=\"p-184733-elevate-2024-is-coming-and-for-the-first-time-our-conference-is-in-person-2\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-184733-elevate-2024-is-coming-and-for-the-first-time-our-conference-is-in-person-2\"></a>Elevate 2024 is coming, and for the first time, our conference is in PERSON!!!</h4>\n<p>Join us for our yearly community gathering created for <em>YOU</em> – our valued community. This year, we’re bringing the community into the spotlight like never before with a community lounge and content based on your feedback.</p>\n<p><strong>Locations</strong>:</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/d/d/ddf3e326860ff014517b3b0bdf4515188f6e614e.png\" alt=\"🇬🇧\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /> London: September 11- 12<br />\n<img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/3/9/390500cd9839b41481d42fcdbe1cebcea813992d.png\" alt=\"🇺🇸\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /> New York City: September 24-25<br />\n<img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/f/c/fc26206db463d61a244f24d493696e95ce33ecd4.png\" alt=\"🇦🇺\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /> Sydney: Oct 22</p>\n<p>But that’s not all – our community has first access to our Early Bird tickets! <img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/d/4/d4c5ede3dac9cb07947179b03f4ec48c26c8f26b.png\" alt=\"🎟️\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /> Hurry up; the Early bird discount won’t last forever!  <a href=\"https://monday.com/elevate/location/london/?utm_medium=organic_social&amp;utm_source=community_forum&amp;utm_campaign=1\">Register now.</a></p>\n<p>Looking forward to getting to meet many of you in our exclusive community lounge at Elevate 2024!</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/b/f/bf571264a46040c41317837e06f9a5062071d88c.png\" title=\"Save the date 4x5\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/b/f/bf571264a46040c41317837e06f9a5062071d88c_2_400x500.png\" alt=\"Save the date 4x5\" width=\"400\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Save the date 4x5</span><span class=\"informations\">2304×2880 172 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>"
